      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just dont see the point in getting up tomorrow. the house is so quiet and it feels like i'm just a ghost walking around. everything is just... empty. there's no reason to keep doing this routine when he isn't here to see it. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to end.",
